name: Commemorative Plates: Strange People
description: Lovingly crafted by Little Pig and grandly minted on the Tezos blockchain, this precious plate commemorates the absurdity of our modern times. Grandly produced in Photoshop, it is artisan handcrafted of lustrous pixels to honor a historic moment of peak Dadaism in the environs of Foodmasku & Little Pigs’ DMs. This exquisite work is offered in a limited 10,000 edition run for 36 hours and remaining supplies will be sent straight to hell.
